sources.title: Controsesso (Countersex 1964) Nino Manfredi, Anna Maria Ferrero | Italian Comedy | Full Movie
sources.description:
A vivid assortment consisted of three acts taken from the lives of modern 1960s Italians, always in orbit around the restless theme of sexual inhibition and the pursuit of pleasure in sex.

Original title: Controsesso (1964) AKA: Countersex / Break Uo

Colorized version https://youtu.be/5OP23M02OA4


This film is subtitled in many languages.
Directors: Renato Castellani, Marco Ferreri, Franco Rossi
Writers: Cesare Zavattini, Leonardo Benvenuti, Piero De Bernardi
Stars: Nino Manfredi, Anna Maria Ferrero, Ugo Tognazzi
